<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:06:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>接地：以色列人目前不属于世界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</link><description>特拉维夫的本古里安国际机场空无一人，外国航空公司没有航班飞往这里，以色列人只是梦想着度假</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</guid></item><item><title>“当以色列与哈马斯战争爆发时，Apple TV 要求停止编写剧本”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</link><description>近年来，以色列电视剧在全球越来越受欢迎，广播公司与外国同行达成了大量协议。但自战争爆发以来，合作被冻结，未来的制作也受到质疑。一位生产商警告说：“我们很可能会变得像俄罗斯一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</guid></item><item><title>新调查显示，一名荷兰国民在 2008 年破坏了伊朗核计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</link><description>Stuxnet 是一种导致伊朗核计划瘫痪的恶意软件，据信是由一​​名伊朗工程师释放的。一份具有里程碑意义的新报告显示，这是一名荷兰国民——与摩萨德和中央情报局合作</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯进入新的战争阶段，但仍没有加沙战后计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</link><description>美国和埃及都对未来的加沙政府提出了合法的想法，但以色列似乎拒绝讨论“以色列持续安全控制”之外的未来。战争进入第四个月，未来与战争开始时一样悬而未决</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会释放人质：我看到他们伤害被囚禁的妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</link><description>“我们确切地知道他们在 10 月 7 日做了什么。如果他们有能力做到这一点——他们在 90 天内能做什么？” 19 岁丹妮拉·吉尔博亚 (Daniela Gilboa) 在加沙地带被哈马斯扣为人质，她的母亲说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</guid></item><item><title>70名以色列议员签署动议，驱逐支持国际法院种族灭绝指控的MK</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫议员表示，“虽然那些明确呼吁用火或原子弹摧毁加沙的人坐在内阁会议桌前，但我因“支持针对以色列的武装斗争”的未经证实的指控而面临被驱逐。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 10:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周一在加沙战斗中丧生的九名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</link><description>被杀的士兵是加夫里尔·布鲁姆（Gavriel Bloom），27 岁；大卫·施瓦茨，26；亚基尔·赫克斯特，26 岁； Roi Tal，19 岁。以色列国防军还表示，一名军官和四名预备役军人受重伤；自战争开始以来，已有514名士兵阵亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子在以色列北部的家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</link><description>受害者没有犯罪记录，是以色列阿拉伯社区自 2024 年初以来的第三名凶杀案受害者。警方怀疑枪击动机与他在灰色市场获得的一笔贷款有关</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 08:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提醒以色列，加沙战争尚未结束，北方紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</link><description>以色列用英语和希伯来语窃窃私语，加沙战争的第三阶段已经开始——从大规模空中和地面战斗转向有针对性的行动 ■ 拉德万部队负责人被暗杀是向真主党高级官员发出的信息■ 布林肯来这里是为了推动加沙和黎巴嫩的解决方案，但他在耶路撒冷的东道主对此表示怀疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，真主党无人机袭击以色列的指挥官在黎巴嫩丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-israeli-leaders-hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-in-lebanon/0000018c-ec30-df6f-ad8e-ec77ad540000</link><description>布林肯会见以色列领导人和战时内阁 ■ 报告：以色列代表团抵达开罗，重启人质释放谈判 ■ 真主党精锐部队高级指挥官在以色列发起的袭击中丧生 ■ 联合国要求追究哈马斯针对以色列平民的性暴力行为 ■ 三人死亡加沙南部拉法附近的车内空袭 ■ 以色列国防军主席称战争将持续一整年</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 03:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-israeli-leaders-hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-in-lebanon/0000018c-ec30-df6f-ad8e-ec77ad540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 Netflix 热门节目《Fauda》的明星在加沙战斗中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/star-of-hit-israeli-netflix-show-fauda-severely-wounded-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-eb27-da45-abbf-eb6795690000</link><description>伊丹·阿梅迪是以色列国防军工程兵的预备役士兵，10月7日后被征召入伍，战争期间随部队在加沙执行任务</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/star-of-hit-israeli-netflix-show-fauda-severely-wounded-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-eb27-da45-abbf-eb6795690000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日三个月后，联合国向以色列派遣性暴力代表</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/three-months-after-october-7-un-sending-sexual-violence-representative-to-israel/0000018c-eb14-da45-abbf-eb741aa90000</link><description>毛里求斯律师普拉米拉·帕滕是首位为此目的派往以色列的联合国官员，应外交部邀请并被授予调查权</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:14:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/three-months-after-october-7-un-sending-sexual-violence-representative-to-israel/0000018c-eb14-da45-abbf-eb741aa90000</guid></item><item><title>巴拉克的任命是以色列在国际法院的防弹衣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/baraks-appointment-is-a-flak-jacket-for-israel-at-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-eaa5-df6f-ad8e-eae78ea10000</link><description>这位前首席大法官的国际地位和独特的历史使他成为针对以色列种族灭绝指控案件的正确任命。但重要的是，他所代表的价值观不仅在外部得到体现，而且在国内得到真正的接受</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 21:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/baraks-appointment-is-a-flak-jacket-for-israel-at-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-eaa5-df6f-ad8e-eae78ea10000</guid></item><item><title>阿米猜·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 辞去以色列社会平等部长职务，将继续担任侨民事务部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</link><description>该部长通知以色列总理，他将辞去职务，因为内塔尼亚胡政府因在战争期间维持 31 个办公室而浪费资源而受到公众批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>“现实已经暂停”：来自以色列加沙前线和黎巴嫩边境的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</link><description>国土报记者安谢尔·普费弗（Anshel Pfeffer）和巴尔·佩莱格（Bar Peleg）最近加入了驻加沙城和黎巴嫩边境的以色列国防军部队。他们的快讯讲述了来自各种可能背景的以色列人的故事，他们的生活在三个月前发生了巨大的变化</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列转向对叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的目标进行更致命的打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israel-shifts-to-deadlier-strikes-on-iran-linked-targets-in-syria-sources-say/0000018c-ea56-df6f-ad8e-ea776a280000</link><description>尽管以色列多年来一直在叙利亚袭击与伊朗有关的目标，但据多个消息来源称，以色列现在对叙利亚境内的伊朗武器转运和防空系统发动了更致命、更频繁的空袭</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israel-shifts-to-deadlier-strikes-on-iran-linked-targets-in-syria-sources-say/0000018c-ea56-df6f-ad8e-ea776a280000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯地道、伏击和友军火力的恐惧：加沙城以色列国防军士兵的 24 小时生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-tunnels-ambushes-and-fear-of-friendly-fire-24-hours-with-idf-soldiers-in-gaza-city/0000018c-e8cd-d765-ab9d-f8fdd47b0000</link><description>在Shujaiyeh的大部分时间都是在等待中度过，每次回家都是经过精心计划的，敌人从地洞里钻出来的危险时刻存在。这些以色列国防军预备役军人现役已进入第四个月，距离纳哈尔奥兹只有五分钟路程</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:44:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-tunnels-ambushes-and-fear-of-friendly-fire-24-hours-with-idf-soldiers-in-gaza-city/0000018c-e8cd-d765-ab9d-f8fdd47b0000</guid></item><item><title>八家外国航空公司将于下个月恢复飞往以色列的部分航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/eight-foreign-airlines-to-resume-partial-service-to-israel-over-the-next-month/0000018c-e9f7-d0e9-a3de-ffff05800000</link><description>如果安全局势恶化，包括法航、波兰LOT和西班牙Vueling在内的八家公司预计将撤回重新启动服务的决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/eight-foreign-airlines-to-resume-partial-service-to-israel-over-the-next-month/0000018c-e9f7-d0e9-a3de-ffff05800000</guid></item><item><title>科学发现猪节食的秘密</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/science-discovers-secret-of-dieting-in-pigs/0000018c-e9d8-d249-a1ce-efdd11220000</link><description>研究表明，胶囊内的微型电机可以欺骗胃，让其误以为它已经吃饱了，从而导致猪吃得更少，虽然很小，但很有趣</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/science-discovers-secret-of-dieting-in-pigs/0000018c-e9d8-d249-a1ce-efdd11220000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织发布了以色列在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-islamic-jihad-publishes-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e9c3-d249-a1ce-efc727f50000</link><description>10 月 7 日，47 岁的埃拉德·卡齐尔 (Elad Katzir) 和他的母亲汉娜 (Hanna) 在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 的家中被绑架，随后汉娜作为人质交易的一部分被释放。他的父亲拉米在袭击中被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-islamic-jihad-publishes-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e9c3-d249-a1ce-efc727f50000</guid></item></channel></rss>